OL,3,C'It's about release': Why are rage
OL,4,Crooms on the rise across the UK?
OL,6,FThe activity that has become all the
OL,7,Frage.
OL,9,FRage rooms have been labelled as an
OL,10,Fadult playground where people can
OL,11,Fsafely bring their frustrations and
OL,12,Fdestroy objects using tools like
OL,13,Fhammers and bats.
OL,15,FThe idea behind the rooms is to
OL,16,Frelease any negative emotions
OL,17,Fphysically, leading to reduced tension.
