OL,3,C'It's about release': Why are rage
OL,4,Crooms on the rise across the UK?
OL,6,FA few of the objects you might find in
OL,7,Fthe rooms range from glassware to
OL,8,Fkitchen appliances, and computer
OL,9,Fmonitors to coffee tables and chairs.
OL,11,FAlso known as 'wreck rooms' or 'smash
OL,12,Frooms', customers are given protective
OL,13,Fgear, including helmets and heavy-duty
OL,14,Fgloves, in order to have safe fun.
OL,16,FThere are over 20 rage rooms in the
OL,17,Fcountry; both fixed locations and pop-
OL,18,Fup events happen throughout the year.
