OL,6,FITV News found prices of rage rooms
OL,7,Ffrom #27 to #200 for half an hour,
OL,8,Fdepending on the number of
OL,9,Fparticipants and items available to
OL,10,Fsmash.
OL,12,FMel Rafferty is a regular customer at
OL,13,FSmash It Rage Room London.
OL,15,FShe told ITV News the reason for her
OL,16,Ffrequent attendance: "I enjoy coming
OL,17,Fdown here on the odd once a month.
OL,18,FJust to let out daily stress that
OL,19,Fhappens cause obviously it all piles
OL,20,Fup eventually."
