OL,6,FAfter grabbing a wrench and smashing a
OL,7,Ffew glasses and teapots, Mel said, "It
OL,8,Ffelt fantastic."
OL,10,F"It's a massive breath, massive weight
OL,11,Foff my shoulders," she added.
OL,13,FAmelia Smewing and Darren Tofts run
OL,14,FSmash It Rage Room in London and say
OL,15,Fthe rooms are welcome to everyone from
OL,16,Fas young as 12 years old.
OL,18,FAnyone under the age of 18 must be
OL,19,Faccompanied by an adult.
