OL,3,C'It's about release': Why are rage
OL,4,Crooms on the rise across the UK?
OL,6,FMs Smewing told ITV News: "It's not
OL,7,Fjust about rage, it's about release.
OL,9,F"People are being referred to us by
OL,10,FGPs, by psychiatrists, and also from
OL,11,Fcharities.
OL,13,F"We work with many, many charities.
OL,14,FEverybody from sex therapists to
OL,15,Fcharities who get children back with
OL,16,Ftheir dads."
OL,18,FThe inspiration behind Ms Smewing and
OL,19,FMr Tofts' rage room came from a
OL,20,Fpersonal place.
