OL,3,C'It's about release': Why are rage
OL,4,Crooms on the rise across the UK?
OL,6,FMs Smewing explained that the idea was
OL,7,Fborn from her son's experience with
OL,8,Fcomplex post-traumatic stress disorder.
OL,10,FFacing long NHS waiting lists for
OL,11,Fsupport, she and her partner began
OL,12,Flooking for ways they could help from
OL,13,Fhome.
OL,15,FShe said they encouraged him to
OL,16,Fexpress what he was feeling by writing
OL,17,Fit down on a plate before smashing it
OL,18,Fin the garden.
