OL,3,C'It's about release': Why are rage
OL,4,Crooms on the rise across the UK?
OL,6,FAfter opening the rage room, Ms
OL,7,FSmewing said her son later visited the
OL,8,Fspace with his cousin. "The pair had a
OL,9,Fgreat time in there. It really did
OL,10,Fhelp him," she said.
OL,12,FTo understand the benefits of rage
OL,13,Frooms, ITV News spoke with
OL,14,Fpsychotherapist Jennifer Cox, who co-
OL,15,Fhosts the podcast Women Are Mad.
OL,17,FShe explained that feelings of rage
OL,18,Foften act as a signal that something
OL,19,Fin a person's life needs to change and
OL,20,Fshould not be ignored.
